reviewText:
When I first watched this movie, I couldn't run more than 50 feet without getting winded, I was smoking half a pack a day and I didn't have a job.
Now I can't say for sure that this movie is the reason, but within a few months after seeing it, I was employeed, I quit smoking and I can run 2 miles in about 20 minutes.
So much talent. This film is 'must see.'
Awesome suspenseful and stylish indie film!
This is an absolutely incredible film.
